 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_and_Eve\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently lying second of these nations going into the final day, the worst McMahon can finish is as the sixth qualifying nation.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Eve is definitely capable of better performance in terms of the World Championships, but to secure qualification she's had to start races very conservatively just to give herself an advantage,\\\" said Irish Sailing head coach, Rory Fitzpatrick.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999865461591161, \"rank\": 7.0224939325711455e-06, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1768, \"end\": 1784, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Fitzpatrick\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory Fitzpatrick\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Fitzpatrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_Fitzpatrick\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With one more race to go, she's going to keep it simple and get around the track fast.\\\"\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"ht